{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"证明毕达哥拉斯定理","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Examples/MathML_Pythagorean_Theorem","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","hasMathML":true,"sidebarHTML":"\n    <ol>\n        <li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element\">MathML Reference</a></strong>\n\n        \n            </li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\">&lt;math&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\">&lt;menclose&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/merror\">&lt;merror&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\">&lt;mpadded&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom\">&lt;mphantom&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot\">&lt;mroot&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow\">&lt;mrow&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\">&lt;ms&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt\">&lt;msqrt&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\">&lt;mstyle&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\">&lt;munderover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/semantics\">&lt;semantics&gt;</a></li>\n        \n\n        \n    </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>现在，我们来证明毕达哥拉斯定理（勾股定理）：</p>\n\n<p><strong>命题：</strong>在一个直角三角形中，斜边的平方等于其他两边的平方之和。</p>\n\n<p>例如，设 a 和 b 为两直角边，c 为斜边，那么&nbsp;<math><mrow><msup><mi> a </mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo> + </mo> <msup><mi> b </mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo> = </mo> <msup><mi> c </mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </mrow> </math>。</p>\n\n<p><strong><u>证明：</u></strong>&nbsp;我们可以通过代数证明来展示大正方形面积等于内正方形（斜边的平方）加上四个三角形的面积：<math style=\"display: block;\"> <mtable columnalign=\"right center left\"> <mtr> <mtd> <msup> <mrow> <mo> ( </mo> <mi> a </mi> <mo> + </mo> <mi> b </mi> <mo> ) </mo> </mrow> <mn> 2 </mn> </msup> </mtd> <mtd> <mo> = </mo> </mtd> <mtd> <msup><mi> c </mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo> + </mo> <mn> 4 </mn> <mo> ⋅ </mo> <mo>(</mo> <mfrac> <mn> 1 </mn> <mn> 2 </mn> </mfrac> <mi> a </mi><mi> b </mi> <mo>)</mo> </mtd> </mtr> <mtr> <mtd> <msup><mi> a </mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo> + </mo> <mn> 2 </mn><mi> a </mi><mi> b </mi> <mo> + </mo> <msup><mi> b </mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </mtd> <mtd> <mo> = </mo> </mtd> <mtd> <msup><mi> c </mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo> + </mo> <mn> 2 </mn><mi> a </mi><mi> b</mi></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><msup><mi>a </mi><mn>2</mn></msup> <mo> + </mo> <msup><mi> b </mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </mtd> <mtd> <mo> = </mo> </mtd> <mtd> <msup><mi> c </mi><mn>2</mn></msup> </mtd> </mtr> </mtable> </math></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"现在，我们来证明毕达哥拉斯定理（勾股定理）：","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Beweis des Satzes des Pythagoras","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Proving the Pythagorean theorem","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"MathML Pythagorean Theorem","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Preuve du théorème de Pythagore","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"ピタゴラスの定理の証明","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Доказательство теоремы Пифагора","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/mathml/examples/mathml_pythagorean_theorem","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/mathml/examples/mathml_pythagorean_theorem/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML","title":"MathML"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Examples","title":"举个例子"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Examples/MathML_Pythagorean_Theorem","title":"证明毕达哥拉斯定理"}],"pageTitle":"证明毕达哥拉斯定理 - MathML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}